dc_title_s: Park and Ride Locations City of Madison, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents park and ride locations in the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2020. [Park and Ride Locations. Planned indicates locations that are in general areas of priority, but which have NOT had formal discussions or agreements as part of a WisDOT improvement project. This data layer is used by the Dane County Bicycle Map application.]
dc_creator_sm: City of Madison - Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO)
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data, please visit: [https://data-cityofmadison.opendata.arcgis.com/]
